comments.body:
Thanks for opening the issue, @larsks!

We recently did some major improvements to Podman's image code. Podman and Buildah don't share that code, unfortunately. However, we plan to create a high-level image library that Podman, Buildah and also CRI-O can share.

@rhatdan, @baude, can we raise priority for that? It's a building block for the CRI-O/libpod work but went under the radar.
